# Alibaba Bailian (DashScope) — Qwen-VL menu recognition.
# Create an API key in the Bailian console (百炼控制台 → API-KEY), then set
# these in Vercel: Project → Settings → Environment Variables.
# For local dev, copy this file to .env.local and fill in the value.

# Required: your Bailian / DashScope API key (sk-...).
DASHSCOPE_API_KEY=

# Optional: OpenAI-compatible base URL (接入地址). Defaults to the value below.
# DASHSCOPE_BASE_URL=https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/compatible-mode/v1

# Optional: which Qwen-VL model to use. Defaults to qwen-vl-max.
# QWEN_VL_MODEL=qwen-vl-max
